<TITLE>Imagemap Error</TITLE><H1>Imagemap Error</H1>Your client did not send any coordinates. Either your client doesn't support imagemap or the map file was not accessed as a map.
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT15-B10-41</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA033-000675-B048-409</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.empower.org:80/cpac/about.html 204.71.237.79 19970209181214 text/html 2866
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 18:13:00 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 20-Jun-96 17:25:35 GMT
Content-length: 2681
