http://www.empower.org:80/conservative/cox.html 204.71.237.79 19970209181826 text/html 13833
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 18:19:10 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 21-Jun-96 15:36:29 GMT
