<head>
<title>The Finger Pointing Page</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<a href="/abic/top.map"><img src="/abic/images/top.gif" 
ALT="Americans Back in Charge Foundation" border="0" ISMAP></a>
<blockquote>
<center><h2>The Finger Pointing Page</h2></title>


<p align="right">
<i>"If you can't say something nice,<br>
come sit by me."</i><br>

--Alice Roosevelt Longworth<br>

</p>
<p>
Last Tuesday (July 16th), the U.S. House voted on whether to raise congressional salaries.  By a vote of 352 to 67, the House decided not to raise their own salaries this year.  This week, ABICF wants to <b>point fingers</b> at the 67 members who felt they were doing such a great job that they deserved a payraise.</p>
<p>
<img src="/abic/images/rt.gif" ALIGN="left" ALT="Finger Pointing Right">
<img src="/abic/images/l.gif" ALIGN="right" ALT="Finger Pointing Left">
It is interesting to note that of the 67, over half have served more than twelve years and 17 have served more than 20 years!!  No wonder that 78% of them voted against term limits last year!</p> 
<p>
There are 48 Democrats and 19 Republicans on this list.  And the vast majority of these members have little fear of losing their jobs over this vote.  Of the 67, only five come from vulnerable seats, winning their 1994 reelection races with less than 55% of the vote.  
<img src="/abic/images/lup.gif" ALIGN="right" ALT="Finger Pointing Up and Left">
<img src="/abic/images/rtup.gif" ALIGN="left" ALT="Finger Pointing Up and Right">
And of those five, four aren't running this year!  So almost all of these members knew not only that they were safe in voting to give themselves a payraise but that they'd be around for a while to enjoy it!</p>
<p>
So ABICF is pointing the finger at each of these members this week because we thought you'd want to know!</p>
<p>
<i>The map below shows the states which have members on the list.  Just click on your state to see the list of members from your congressional delegation who voted to raise their salaries.</i></p>
<center>
<a href="/abic/images/ptf-7-22-96.map"><img src="/abic/images/ptf-7-22-96.gif" border="0" ISMAP></a>
<p>
You can also see the <a href="/abic/ptf/7-22-96a.html.cgi">complete list</a> of members who voted to raise their salaries.
</center>
<p>
<center>
<a href="/abic/ftb/">Footing the Bill</a> - <a href="/abic/ptf/">Pointing the Finger</a> - <a href="/abic/sbg/welcome.html.cgi">Spotlight on Big Government</a><br>
<a href="/abic/new.html.cgi">What's New?</a> - <a href="/abic/about.html.cgi">About ABIC</a> - <a href="/abic/features.html.cgi">Features</a> - <a href="/abic/links.html.cgi">Links</a> - <a href="/abic/listserv.html.cgi">ListServ</a><br>
