<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<a href="/abic/top.map"><img src="/abic/images/top.gif" border="0" ALT="Americans Back in Charge" ISMAP></a><p>
<center><h2>Citizenship Calendar</h2>
<h3>September 29 - November 9, 1996</h3>
</center>
<P>
One of the best ways for Americans to take charge
is to stay informed on upcoming events and participate in them
as they happen in your area! So check the calendar often to see
what's coming up soon!<BR>

<P>
The items on the calendar will become links as information
is added to the site about each event.  The calendar will be updated
each week.  If you have a major event to suggest, please <a href="mailto:abic@abic.org">e-mail</a>
the information to us and we'll consider posting it!<BR>

